---
title: Cheesy Sausage & Kale Flatbreads with Red Onion & Chili Flakes
description: Get ready to make delicious, foolproof, homemade flatbread pizza! And not just any pizza—these are sprinkled with mellow Monterey Jack and an Italian cheese blend, then topped with browned pork sausage and tender sautéed kale and red onion. Sprinkle your masterpiece with chili flakes, then broil until bubbly and dig right in!
